{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1772871921479,"sessionID":"ses_3389967ebffeq10PXnV18VW536","part":{"id":"prt_cc766af35001UwzzNnONMOmSmY","sessionID":"ses_3389967ebffeq10PXnV18VW536","messageID":"msg_cc766982f001Dft45fOm3aToMv","type":"tool","callID":"call_e564d2c3de694cb9b2e29320","tool":"read","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/sonnet/opencode/SG-AgentTeam/practice/status/task-assignments/v1.1-task-assignments.md"},"output":"<path>/Users/sonnet/opencode/SG-AgentTeam/practice/status/task-assignments/v1.1-task-assignments.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>1: # v1.1 Task Assignments\n2: \n3: **Version**: v1.1  \n4: **Sprint**: Sprint 1-3 (6 weeks)  \n5: **Created**: 2026-03-06  \n6: **Owner**: PM Team  \n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Overview\n11: \n12: This document outlines the task assignments for v1.1 development, following the correct architecture where **opencode is the master agent** and **knowledge-assistant provides specialized tools**.\n13: \n14: ---\n15: \n16: ## Architecture Summary\n17: \n18: ```\n19: opencode (Master)\n20:   ├── File operations (own capability)\n21:   ├── NLU & intent understanding (own capability)\n22:   └── Calls knowledge-assistant tools\n23:       ↓\n24: knowledge-assistant (Tool Library)\n25:   ├── build_semantic_index(documents) → IndexResult\n26:   ├── semantic_search(query) → [SearchResult]\n27:   ├── extract_keywords(content) → [Keyword]\n28:   └── EmailConnector → Email data\n29: ```\n30: \n31: ---\n32: \n33: ## Sprint Plan\n34: \n35: ### Sprint 1 (Week 1-2): Core Indexing & Search\n36: \n37: **Goal**: Build semantic indexing and search capabilities\n38: \n39: **Deliverables**:\n40: - Semantic index builder\n41: - Semantic search tool\n42: - Basic tests\n43: \n44: ### Sprint 2 (Week 3-4): Extraction & Connectors\n45: \n46: **Goal**: Add knowledge extraction and email integration\n47: \n48: **Deliverables**:\n49: - Keyword extraction\n50: - Summary generation\n51: - Email connector\n52: - Integration tests\n53: \n54: ### Sprint 3 (Week 5-6): Integration & Release\n55: \n56: **Goal**: Integrate with opencode and release v1.1\n57: \n58: **Deliverables**:\n59: - Skill definition\n60: - Agent configuration\n61: - Documentation\n62: - v1.1 release\n63: \n64: ---\n65: \n66: ## Team Assignments\n67: \n68: ### Data Team\n69: \n70: **Sprint 1 Tasks**:\n71: \n72: #### TASK-D1: Semantic Index Builder\n73: **Priority**: P0  \n74: **Estimated Effort**: 5 days  \n75: **Dependencies**: None  \n76: \n77: **Description**: Implement `build_semantic_index()` function\n78: \n79: **Requirements**:\n80: - Input: List of document data (path, content, metadata) from opencode\n81: - Process: Generate embeddings, build FAISS index\n82: - Output: IndexResult with statistics\n83: - NO file scanning or reading (opencode provides data)\n84: \n85: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n86: - [ ] Function accepts document list\n87: - [ ] Generates vector embeddings\n88: - [ ] Builds FAISS index\n89: - [ ] Saves index to disk\n90: - [ ] Returns structured result\n91: - [ ] Unit tests > 85% coverage\n92: - [ ] Performance: 1000 docs < 30s\n93: \n94: **Files to Create/Modify**:\n95: ```\n96: scripts/\n97: ├── embeddings/\n98: │   ├── __init__.py\n99: │   ├── encoder.py              # NEW: Embedding encoder\n100: │   └── models.py               # NEW: Model management\n101: ├── index/\n102: │   ├── __init__.py\n103: │   ├── vector_store.py         # NEW: FAISS vector store\n104: │   └── manager.py              # NEW: Index manager\n105: └── tools/\n106:     ├── __init__.py\n107:     └── indexing.py             # NEW: build_semantic_index()\n108: ```\n109: \n110: **API Example**:\n111: ```python\n112: from scripts.tools.indexing import build_semantic_index\n113: \n114: # opencode provides document data\n115: documents = [\n116:     {\n117:         \"path\": \"D:/notes/python.md\",\n118:         \"content\": \"...\",\n119:         \"metadata\": {\"title\": \"...\", \"date\": \"...\"}\n120:     }\n121: ]\n122: \n123: result = build_semantic_index(\n124:     documents=documents,\n125:     index_path=\".ka-index\"\n126: )\n127: \n128: # Returns\n129: {\n130:     \"success\": True,\n131:     \"total_docs\": 156,\n132:     \"total_chunks\": 489,\n133:     \"index_size\": \"23.5 MB\",\n134:     \"build_time\": \"12.3s\"\n135: }\n136: ```\n137: \n138: ---\n139: \n140: #### TASK-D2: Semantic Search Tool\n141: **Priority**: P0  \n142: **Estimated Effort**: 3 days  \n143: **Dependencies**: TASK-D1  \n144: \n145: **Description**: Implement `semantic_search()` function\n146: \n147: **Requirements**:\n148: - Input: Query text, index path, filters\n149: - Process: Query embedding, vector search\n150: - Output: List of SearchResult (path, similarity, snippet)\n151: \n152: **Acceptance Criteria**:\n153: - [ ] Loads index from disk\n154: - [ ] Generates query embedding\n155: - [ ] Performs vector search\n156: - [ ] Returns ranked results with snippets\n157: - [ ] Supports metadata filtering\n158: - [ ] Unit tests > 85% coverage\n159: \n160: **Files to Create**:\n161: ```\n162: scripts/tools/search.py         # NEW: semantic_search()\n163: ```\n164: \n165: **API Example**:\n166: ```python\n167: from scripts.tools.search import semantic_search\n168: \n169: results = semantic_search(\n170:     query=\"Python async programming\",\n171:     index_path=\".ka-index\",\n172:     top_k=5\n173: )\n174: \n175: # Returns\n176: [\n177:     {\n178:         \"path\": \"D:/notes/python.md\",\n179:         \"similarity\": 0.89,\n180:         \"snippet\": \"...\",\n181:         \"metadata\": {...}\n182:     }\n183: ]\n184: ```\n185: \n186: ---\n187: \n188: **Sprint 2 Tasks**:\n189: \n190: #### TASK-D3: Keyword Extraction\n191: **Priority**: P1  \n192: **Estimated Effort**: 2 days  \n193: **Dependencies**: None  \n194: \n195: **Description**: Implement `extract_keywords()` function\n196: \n197: **Requirements**:\n198: - Support TF-IDF method\n199: - Support TextRank method\n200: - Return top-N keywords with scores\n201: \n202: **Files to Create**:\n203: ```\n204: scripts/tools/extraction.py     # NEW: extract_keywords()\n205: ```\n206: \n207: ---\n208: \n209: #### TASK-D4: Summary Generation\n210: **Priority**: P1  \n211: **Estimated Effort**: 2 days  \n212: **Dependencies**: None  \n213: \n214: **Description**: Implement `generate_summary()` function\n215: \n216: **Requirements**:\n217: - Extractive summarization\n218: - Configurable length\n219: - Preserve key information\n220: \n221: **Files to Modify**:\n222: ```\n223: scripts/tools/extraction.py     # ADD: generate_summary()\n224: ```\n225: \n226: ---\n227: \n228: #### TASK-D5: Email Connector\n229: **Priority**: P1  \n230: **Estimated Effort**: 3 days  \n231: **Dependencies**: None  \n232: \n233: **Description**: Implement email connection and search\n234: \n235: **Requirements**:\n236: - IMAP connection\n237: - Fetch email summaries\n238: - Search emails by keyword\n239: - Return structured email data\n240: \n241: **Files to Create**:\n242: ```\n243: scripts/connectors/\n244: ├── __init__.py\n245: ├── base.py                     # NEW: BaseConnector class\n246: └── email.py                    # NEW: EmailConnector class\n247: ```\n248: \n249: **API Example**:\n250: ```python\n251: from scripts.connectors.email import EmailConnector\n252: \n253: connector = EmailConnector(server, username, password)\n254: connector.connect()\n255: \n256: emails = connector.search_emails(\"project budget\")\n257: \n258: # Returns\n259: [\n260:     {\n261:         \"id\": \"msg_123\",\n262:         \"subject\": \"...\",\n263:         \"from\": \"...\",\n264:         \"date\": \"...\",\n265:         \"snippet\": \"...\"\n266:     }\n267: ]\n268: ```\n269: \n270: ---\n271: \n272: ### Template Team\n273: \n274: **Sprint 3 Tasks**:\n275: \n276: #### TASK-T1: Skill Definition\n277: **Priority**: P0  \n278: **Estimated Effort**: 3 days  \n279: **Dependencies**: TASK-D1, TASK-D2  \n280: \n281: **Description**: Create SKILL.md for knowledge-assistant\n282: \n283: **Requirements**:\n284: - Define skill triggers and patterns\n285: - Document tool functions\n286: - Provide usage examples\n287: - Integration with opencode\n288: \n289: **Files to Create**:\n290: ```\n291: skills/knowledge-assistant/\n292: └── SKILL.md                    # NEW: Skill definition\n293: ```\n294: \n295: **Content Requirements**:\n296: - Trigger phrases (e.g., \"search knowledge\", \"build knowledge base\")\n297: - Tool function documentation\n298: - Input/output specifications\n299: - Usage patterns and examples\n300: \n301: ---\n302: \n303: #### TASK-T2: Agent Configuration\n304: **Priority**: P0  \n305: **Estimated Effort**: 2 days  \n306: **Dependencies**: TASK-T1  \n307: \n308: **Description**: Create AGENT.md for knowledge-assistant agent\n309: \n310: **Requirements**:\n311: - Define agent capabilities\n312: - Map intents to tools\n313: - Document interaction patterns\n314: - Configuration details\n315: \n316: **Files to Create**:\n317: ```\n318: AGENT.md                        # NEW: Agent configuration\n319: ```\n320: \n321: **Content Requirements**:\n322: - Agent overview and capabilities\n323: - Intent → Tool mapping\n324: - Workflow descriptions\n325: - Usage examples\n326: - Configuration guide\n327: \n328: ---\n329: \n330: ### Test Team\n331: \n332: **Sprint 1 Tasks**:\n333: \n334: #### TASK-TE1: Index Building Tests\n335: **Priority**: P0  \n336: **Estimated Effort**: 2 days  \n337: **Dependencies**: TASK-D1  \n338: \n339: **Description**: Test semantic index builder\n340: \n341: **Files to Create**:\n342: ```\n343: tests/\n344: ├── test_embeddings.py          # NEW: Encoder tests\n345: ├── test_vector_store.py        # NEW: Vector store tests\n346: └── test_indexing.py            # NEW: Index building tests\n347: ```\n348: \n349: ---\n350: \n351: #### TASK-TE2: Search Tests\n352: **Priority**: P0  \n353: **Estimated Effort**: 2 days  \n354: **Dependencies**: TASK-D2  \n355: \n356: **Description**: Test semantic search\n357: \n358: **Files to Create**:\n359: ```\n360: tests/test_search.py            # NEW: Search tests\n361: ```\n362: \n363: ---\n364: \n365: **Sprint 2 Tasks**:\n366: \n367: #### TASK-TE3: Extraction Tests\n368: **Priority**: P1  \n369: **Estimated Effort**: 2 days  \n370: **Dependencies**: TASK-D3, TASK-D4  \n371: \n372: **Description**: Test extraction tools\n373: \n374: **Files to Create**:\n375: ```\n376: tests/test_extraction.py        # NEW: Extraction tests\n377: ```\n378: \n379: ---\n380: \n381: #### TASK-TE4: Connector Tests\n382: **Priority**: P1  \n383: **Estimated Effort**: 2 days  \n384: **Dependencies**: TASK-D5  \n385: \n386: **Description**: Test email connector\n387: \n388: **Files to Create**:\n389: ```\n390: tests/test_connectors.py        # NEW: Connector tests\n391: ```\n392: \n393: ---\n394: \n395: **Sprint 3 Tasks**:\n396: \n397: #### TASK-TE5: Integration Tests\n398: **Priority**: P0  \n399: **Estimated Effort**: 3 days  \n400: **Dependencies**: All previous tasks  \n401: \n402: **Description**: Integration tests for opencode usage\n403: \n404: **Files to Create**:\n405: ```\n406: tests/integration/\n407: ├── test_opencode_integration.py    # NEW\n408: └── test_full_workflow.py           # NEW\n409: ```\n410: \n411: ---\n412: \n413: ### PM Team\n414: \n415: **Sprint 1-3 Tasks**:\n416: \n417: #### TASK-PM1: Documentation\n418: **Priority**: P1  \n419: **Estimated Effort**: Ongoing  \n420: \n421: **Description**: Update documentation for v1.1\n422: \n423: **Files to Update**:\n424: ```\n425: docs/\n426: ├── PRD.md                      # UPDATE: Reflect correct architecture\n427: ├── api-reference.md            # UPDATE: Add new APIs\n428: └── user-guide.md               # UPDATE: Add new features\n429: \n430: README.md                       # UPDATE: New capabilities\n431: RELEASE_NOTES.md                # CREATE: v1.1 release notes\n432: ```\n433: \n434: ---\n435: \n436: #### TASK-PM2: Release Management\n437: **Priority**: P0  \n438: **Estimated Effort**: Sprint 3  \n439: \n440: **Description**: Prepare and execute v1.1 release\n441: \n442: **Deliverables**:\n443: - [ ] Release notes\n444: - [ ] Documentation complete\n445: - [ ] All tests passing\n446: - [ ] GitHub release\n447: \n448: ---\n449: \n450: ## Dependencies Graph\n451: \n452: ```\n453: Sprint 1:\n454: TASK-D1 (Index) ──→ TASK-D2 (Search) ──→ TASK-TE1, TASK-TE2 (Tests)\n455:     │\n456:     └───────────────→ TASK-PM1 (Docs)\n457: \n458: Sprint 2:\n459: TASK-D3 (Keywords) ──→ TASK-TE3 (Tests)\n460: TASK-D4 (Summary)  ──→ TASK-TE3 (Tests)\n461: TASK-D5 (Email)    ──→ TASK-TE4 (Tests)\n462: \n463: Sprint 3:\n464: TASK-D1, D2 ──→ TASK-T1 (Skill) ──→ TASK-T2 (Agent)\n465: All tasks    ──→ TASK-TE5 (Integration)\n466: All tasks    ──→ TASK-PM2 (Release)\n467: ```\n468: \n469: ---\n470: \n471: ## Milestones\n472: \n473: ### M7: Index & Search (End of Sprint 1)\n474: - [ ] TASK-D1: Index builder complete\n475: - [ ] TASK-D2: Search tool complete\n476: - [ ] TASK-TE1, TE2: Tests passing\n477: - [ ] Coverage > 85%\n478: \n479: ### M8: Extraction & Connectors (End of Sprint 2)\n480: - [ ] TASK-D3, D4: Extraction complete\n481: - [ ] TASK-D5: Email connector complete\n482: - [ ] TASK-TE3, TE4: Tests passing\n483: - [ ] Coverage > 85%\n484: \n485: ### M9: Integration (End of Sprint 3)\n486: - [ ] TASK-T1: Skill definition complete\n487: - [ ] TASK-T2: Agent config complete\n488: - [ ] TASK-TE5: Integration tests passing\n489: - [ ] Documentation complete\n490: \n491: ### M10: Release (End of Sprint 3)\n492: - [ ] All tasks complete\n493: - [ ] All tests passing\n494: - [ ] Documentation reviewed\n495: - [ ] v1.1 released\n496: \n497: ---\n498: \n499: ## Risks & Mitigation\n500: \n501: | Risk | Impact | Mitigation |\n502: |------|--------|------------|\n503: | Embedding model size | Medium | Use smaller model, document requirements |\n504: | Email API changes | Low | Use stable APIs, add error handling |\n505: | Integration complexity | Medium | Start integration early (Sprint 3 week 1) |\n506: \n507: ---\n508: \n509: ## Communication Plan\n510: \n511: ### Weekly Updates\n512: - PM Team updates `agent-status.md` every Friday\n513: - Teams report blockers in GitHub Issues\n514: \n515: ### Sprint Reviews\n516: - End of Sprint 1: Demo index & search\n517: - End of Sprint 2: Demo extraction & email\n518: - End of Sprint 3: Full demo & release\n519: \n520: ---\n521: \n522: ## Next Steps\n523: \n524: 1. **PM Team**: Create GitHub Issues for each task\n525: 2. **Data Team**: Start TASK-D1 (Semantic Index Builder)\n526: 3. **Test Team**: Prepare test fixtures\n527: 4. **Template Team**: Review skill design requirements\n528: \n529: ---\n530: \n531: **Created by**: PM Team  \n532: **Date**: 2026-03-06  \n533: **Status**: Ready for Assignment\n\n(End of file - total 533 lines)\n</content>","title":"practice/status/task-assignments/v1.1-task-assignments.md","metadata":{"preview":"# v1.1 Task Assignments\n\n**Version**: v1.1  \n**Sprint**: Sprint 1-3 (6 weeks)  \n**Created**: 2026-03-06  \n**Owner**: PM Team  \n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nThis document outlines the task assignments for v1.1 development, following the correct architecture where **opencode is the master agent** and **knowledge-assistant provides specialized tools**.\n\n---\n\n## Architecture Summary\n\n```\nopencode (Master)\n  ├── File operations (own capability)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"time":{"start":1772871921470,"end":1772871921478}}}}
